{"tid":1671474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[tg當炸彈] 中國製催淚彈 炸死泰國示威者","createTime":"2019-10-23T13:25:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T00:56:22.000Z","uid":52658,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0e3538f36ea7c71158a11529ce3002f7297cae5c","tid":1671474,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T13:25:59.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】泰國防暴警察上周在曼谷國會大樓外，用催淚彈驅散反政府示威者，造成3死400多人傷。調查人員指出，警方當天所使用的廉價<span style=\"color: red;\">中國製催淚彈含炸藥成分</span>，威力足以令地面炸出地面一個坑，相信與導致有人死亡及多人被炸斷手腳有關。泰國警方隨即宣布停用所有中國製催淚彈。<br />\n<br />\n數以千計泰國示威者上周二圍堵國會大樓，企圖阻止首相頌猜發表施政報告，防暴警察其後使用催淚彈驅散人群，造成多人傷亡。泰國人權委員會、中央法醫研究所等組成的專家小組隨即展開調查。法醫研究所負責人蓬提表示，他們在警方當日使用的中國、美國及西班牙製造的6種催淚彈中，發現有3種催淚彈含有高濃度的RDX成分，<span style=\"color: red;\">全部均為中國製造</span>。RDX通常用於製造炸藥，並非催淚彈的標準成分。<br />\n<br />\n痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想殺人啊"},{"pid":"c220fb138ce175d405412d597c6ab44dc9d80467","tid":1671474,"uid":322141,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T13:26:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9767dc45be7c3adf6afe8ca8ba0551e0d4a6d753","tid":1671474,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T13:29:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a0c68f959fdc2ff2bca61ecec6a5b512a8f57a","tid":1671474,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T13:36:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c255f26cfa514d6c8db335ad357cdd633909213f","tid":1671474,"uid":189650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T13:36:51.000Z","msg":"CLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/